194
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:58,870
The Warlord agreed
to help you kill Gu Yanting,

195
00:10:59,910 --> 00:11:02,120
but he didn't want Jiang Ruruo to live.

196
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:16,510
Oh yes.

197
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:17,870
My foster father

198
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:20,510
enjoys having everything in control.

199
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:21,870
I have been informed

200
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:23,750
that he has planted his man
in your mansion.

201
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:36,630
So you are the Warlord's man.

202
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,150
Over the years,

203
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,720
I have never got suspicious of you.

204
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:43,800
Commander,

205
00:11:44,390 --> 00:11:45,600
if you stuck with the plan

206
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:47,720
and helped the Warlord
occupy Jiangcheng,

207
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:50,120
I'd still be loyal to you.

208
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,080
All he wants is the city,

209
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,910
but why Ruruo's death?

210
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,440
It's simple.

211
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:01,480
He doesn't want her alive.

212
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:05,480
What's the story between them?

213
