to approach her

215
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:17,440
in an attempt to obtain
the treasure map.

216
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,790
However, Gu Yanting
fell in love with her,

217
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,870
and returned to Ningcheng empty-handed.

218
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:24,910
The Warlord's plan failed,

219
00:12:25,790 --> 00:12:27,510
