220
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,120
Seven years ago,

221
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,840
the Warlord sent Yanting over.

222
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,870
But unexpectedly,
a stone-hearted man like you

223
00:12:37,790 --> 00:12:39,320
would get soft for her.

224
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:42,120
You even gave away the Armory.

225
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:44,870
So now you see?

226
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:47,000
The Warlord decides

227
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,080
this woman must go!

228
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,040
Xiao Li,

229
00:13:00,790 --> 00:13:03,670
you set me up.

230
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:07,960
(Yanting is not dead.)

231
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:09,750
(I must find him.)

232
00:13:13,750 --> 00:13:15,910
Now that the Warlord's spy is killed,

233
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,390
starting now,

234
00:13:22,270 --> 00:13:24,480
Jiangcheng will be mine.

235
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:35,110
Ruruo,

236
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:36,670
from this day on,

237
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,320
you go nowhere.

238
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,000
You stay by my side

239
00:13:41,750 --> 00:13:43,270
as the commander's wife.

240
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:01,230
Ruruo,

241
00:14:01,790 --> 00:14:02,790
