242
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:07,710
Xiao Li,

243
00:14:08,630 --> 00:14:09,670
I'd rather die

244
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:12,080
than be with you.

245
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,270
Don't hurt yourself.

246
00:14:15,630 --> 00:14:16,470
Xiao Li.

